This paper focuses on efficient parallel algorithms for the key machine learning task of inference on graphical models, specifically on the belief propagation algorithm. This task is closely related to topics in machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
